text: Club Deportivo Móstoles U.R.J.C., formerly CDE El Soto and CD Juventud Móstoles, is a Spanish football team based in Móstoles, in the autonomous community of Madrid. Founded in 1996, it plays in Tercera División, holding home games at Estadio El Soto, which has about 14,000-seat capacity. == History == CD Móstoles URJC was founded on June 14, 1996, firstly with
